### outcome.decision
If a decision was made in this turn:
- **decision**: Short identifier (e.g., "adopt-single-submsgtype")
- **decisionRationale**: Why this decision was made
- **impact**: How this affects design/implementation/etc
- **blockers**: Any issues that need to be resolved

