## Comparison: Wrong vs Correct

### ❌ WRONG (Truncated)
```json
{
  "user": {
    "message": "为什么要新增两个subMsgType?..."  // ❌ Truncated
  },
  "ai": {
    "message": "这是个非常好的问题!让我分析...",  // ❌ Truncated
    "fileChanges": []  // ❌ No details
  }
}
```

**Problem**: 
- User's full question lost
- AI's complete analysis lost
- No record of what was actually changed

### ✅ CORRECT (Complete)
```json
{
  "user": {
    "message": "为什么要新增两个subMsgType?我们这个场景是不是只需要一个就行,基于这一个新增的subMsgType,配置几个contentKey就行了吧?",  // ✅ Complete
    "messageLength": 68
  },
  "ai": {
    "message": "[2341 characters of complete response including:\n- Code analysis of UnifiedMessageTypeConverter\n- Explanation of subMsgType vs contentKey roles\n- Comparison table\n- Recommendation with rationale\n- Implementation examples]",  // ✅ Complete
    "messageLength": 2341,
    "codeSnippets": [
      {
        "file": "UnifiedMessageTypeConverter.java",
        "snippet": "public String matchMessageTypeByValue(int value) {...}"
      }
    ],
    "fileChanges": [
      {
        "file": "design.md",
        "changes": [
          {
            "type": "deletion",
            "description": "Removed REFUSED_TO_JOIN enum",
            "contentBefore": "CHANNEL_SYSTEM_MESSAGE_REFUSED_TO_JOIN(45015, ...)"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

**Result**:
- Full conversational context preserved
- Complete reasoning and code analysis saved
- Detailed record of all file modifications
- Resume can reconstruct exact work done

